subject: Poetry collection
msgSnippet: Why don t we all upload our favourite poems in Quikscript? We could have some sort of poetry collection, which would be a real help for learners. Personally,
messageBody:
Why don't we all upload our favourite poems in Quikscript? We could
have some sort of poetry collection, which would be a real help for
learners. Personally, I've already uploaded Jabberwocky, The
Three-toed Grynch by Odgen Nash and The Garden of Proserpine by
Algernon Swinbourne.
